Oracle Cloud Infrastructure 生成式 AI¶

Oracle Cloud Infrastructure (OCI) 生成式 AI 是一项全托管服务，提供一系列最先进、可定制的大型语言模型 (LLMs)，覆盖广泛的使用场景，并通过单一 API 即可使用。借助 OCI 生成式 AI 服务，您可以访问开箱即用的预训练模型，或在专用 AI 集群上基于自有数据创建和托管经过微调的自定义模型。该服务及 API 的详细文档请参阅 此处 和 此处。

本笔记本将说明如何通过 LlamaIndex 使用 OCI 的生成式 AI 模型。

安装配置¶

若您在 Colab 平台上打开此 Notebook，很可能需要先安装 LlamaIndex 🦙。

In [ ]:
Copied! 
%pip install llama-index-llms-oci-genai
%pip install llama-index-llms-oci-genai
In [ ]:
Copied! 
!pip install llama-index
!pip install llama-index

您还需要安装 OCI SDK

In [ ]:
Copied! 
!pip install -U oci
!pip install -U oci

基本用法¶

通过 LlamaIndex 使用 OCI 生成式 AI 提供的 LLM 模型时，您只需使用 OCI 终端节点、模型 ID、OCID 和认证方法初始化 OCIGenAI 接口即可。

调用 complete 方法并传入提示词¶

In [ ]:
Copied! 
from llama_index.llms.oci_genai import OCIGenAI

llm = OCIGenAI(
    model="MY_MODEL",
    service_endpoint="https://inference.generativeai.us-chicago-1.oci.oraclecloud.com",
    compartment_id="MY_OCID",
)

resp = llm.complete("Paul Graham is ")
print(resp)
from llama_index.llms.oci_genai import OCIGenAI llm = OCIGenAI( model="MY_MODEL", service_endpoint="https://inference.generativeai.us-chicago-1.oci.oraclecloud.com", compartment_id="MY_OCID", ) resp = llm.complete("Paul Graham is ") print(resp)

使用消息列表调用 chat 方法¶

In [ ]:
Copied! 
from llama_index.llms.oci_genai import OCIGenAI
from llama_index.core.llms import ChatMessage

messages = [
    ChatMessage(
        role="system", content="You are a pirate with a colorful personality"
    ),
    ChatMessage(role="user", content="Tell me a story"),
]

llm = OCIGenAI(
    model="MY_MODEL",
    service_endpoint="https://inference.generativeai.us-chicago-1.oci.oraclecloud.com",
    compartment_id="MY_OCID",
)

resp = llm.chat(messages)
print(resp)
from llama_index.llms.oci_genai import OCIGenAI from llama_index.core.llms import ChatMessage messages = [ ChatMessage( role="system", content="You are a pirate with a colorful personality" ), ChatMessage(role="user", content="Tell me a story"), ] llm = OCIGenAI( model="MY_MODEL", service_endpoint="https://inference.generativeai.us-chicago-1.oci.oraclecloud.com", compartment_id="MY_OCID", ) resp = llm.chat(messages) print(resp)

from llama_index.llms.oci_genai import OCIGenAI
from llama_index.core.llms import ChatMessage, TextBlock, ImageBlock

messages = [
    ChatMessage(
        role="user",
        blocks=[
            ImageBlock(url=test_image_url),
            TextBlock(text="Describe the image in a few sentences."),
        ],
    )
]

llm = OCIGenAI(
    model="meta.llama-3.2-90b-vision-instruct",
    service_endpoint="https://inference.generativeai.us-chicago-1.oci.oraclecloud.com",
    compartment_id="MY_OCID",
)

resp = llm.chat(messages)
print(resp.message.content)
from llama_index.llms.oci_genai import OCIGenAI from llama_index.core.llms import ChatMessage, TextBlock, ImageBlock messages = [ ChatMessage( role="user", blocks=[ ImageBlock(url=test_image_url), TextBlock(text="Describe the image in a few sentences."), ], ) ] llm = OCIGenAI( model="meta.llama-3.2-90b-vision-instruct", service_endpoint="https://inference.generativeai.us-chicago-1.oci.oraclecloud.com", compartment_id="MY_OCID", ) resp = llm.chat(messages) print(resp.message.content)

流式传输¶

使用 stream_complete 端点

In [ ]:
Copied! 
from llama_index.llms.oci_genai import OCIGenAI

llm = OCIGenAI(
    model="MY_MODEL",
    service_endpoint="https://inference.generativeai.us-chicago-1.oci.oraclecloud.com",
    compartment_id="MY_OCID",
)

resp = llm.stream_complete("Paul Graham is ")
for r in resp:
    print(r.delta, end="")
from llama_index.llms.oci_genai import OCIGenAI llm = OCIGenAI( model="MY_MODEL", service_endpoint="https://inference.generativeai.us-chicago-1.oci.oraclecloud.com", compartment_id="MY_OCID", ) resp = llm.stream_complete("Paul Graham is ") for r in resp: print(r.delta, end="")

使用 stream_chat 端点

In [ ]:
Copied! 
from llama_index.llms.oci_genai import OCIGenAI
from llama_index.core.llms import ChatMessage

messages = [
    ChatMessage(
        role="system", content="You are a pirate with a colorful personality"
    ),
    ChatMessage(role="user", content="Tell me a story"),
]

llm = OCIGenAI(
    model="MY_MODEL",
    service_endpoint="https://inference.generativeai.us-chicago-1.oci.oraclecloud.com",
    compartment_id="MY_OCID",
)

resp = llm.stream_chat(messages)
for r in resp:
    print(r.delta, end="")
from llama_index.llms.oci_genai import OCIGenAI from llama_index.core.llms import ChatMessage messages = [ ChatMessage( role="system", content="You are a pirate with a colorful personality" ), ChatMessage(role="user", content="Tell me a story"), ] llm = OCIGenAI( model="MY_MODEL", service_endpoint="https://inference.generativeai.us-chicago-1.oci.oraclecloud.com", compartment_id="MY_OCID", ) resp = llm.stream_chat(messages) for r in resp: print(r.delta, end="")

异步处理¶

原生异步调用当前不受支持。异步调用将回退至同步模式

In [ ]:
Copied! 
from llama_index.llms.oci_genai import OCIGenAI
from llama_index.core.llms import ChatMessage

messages = [
    ChatMessage(
        role="system", content="You are a pirate with a colorful personality"
    ),
    ChatMessage(role="user", content="Tell me a story"),
]

llm = OCIGenAI(
    model="MY_MODEL",
    service_endpoint="https://inference.generativeai.us-chicago-1.oci.oraclecloud.com",
    compartment_id="MY_OCID",
)

resp = llm.achat(messages)
print(resp)

resp = llm.astream_chat(messages)
for r in resp:
    print(r.delta, end="")
from llama_index.llms.oci_genai import OCIGenAI from llama_index.core.llms import ChatMessage messages = [ ChatMessage( role="system", content="You are a pirate with a colorful personality" ), ChatMessage(role="user", content="Tell me a story"), ] llm = OCIGenAI( model="MY_MODEL", service_endpoint="https://inference.generativeai.us-chicago-1.oci.oraclecloud.com", compartment_id="MY_OCID", ) resp = llm.achat(messages) print(resp) resp = llm.astream_chat(messages) for r in resp: print(r.delta, end="")

配置模型¶

In [ ]:
Copied! 
from llama_index.llms.oci_genai import OCIGenAI

llm = OCIGenAI(
    model="cohere.command",
    service_endpoint="https://inference.generativeai.us-chicago-1.oci.oraclecloud.com",
    compartment_id="MY_OCID",
)

resp = llm.complete("Paul Graham is ")
print(resp)
from llama_index.llms.oci_genai import OCIGenAI llm = OCIGenAI( model="cohere.command", service_endpoint="https://inference.generativeai.us-chicago-1.oci.oraclecloud.com", compartment_id="MY_OCID", ) resp = llm.complete("Paul Graham is ") print(resp)

认证¶

LlamaIndex 支持的认证方法与其它 OCI 服务相同，遵循 标准 SDK 认证 方式，具体包括 API 密钥、会话令牌、实例主体和资源主体。

API 密钥是默认认证方式。以下示例展示了如何使用其他认证方法（会话令牌）

In [ ]:
Copied! 
from llama_index.llms.oci_genai import OCIGenAI

llm = OCIGenAI(
    model="MY_MODEL",
    service_endpoint="https://inference.generativeai.us-chicago-1.oci.oraclecloud.com",
    compartment_id="MY_OCID",
    auth_type="SECURITY_TOKEN",
    auth_profile="MY_PROFILE",  # replace with your profile name
    auth_file_location="MY_CONFIG_FILE_LOCATION",  # replace with file location where profile name configs present
)

resp = llm.complete("Paul Graham is ")
print(resp)
from llama_index.llms.oci_genai import OCIGenAI llm = OCIGenAI( model="MY_MODEL", service_endpoint="https://inference.generativeai.us-chicago-1.oci.oraclecloud.com", compartment_id="MY_OCID", auth_type="SECURITY_TOKEN", auth_profile="MY_PROFILE", # replace with your profile name auth_file_location="MY_CONFIG_FILE_LOCATION", # replace with file location where profile name configs present ) resp = llm.complete("Paul Graham is ") print(resp)

专属 AI 集群¶

要访问托管在专属 AI 集群中的模型，请先__创建端点__，系统分配的 OCID（当前前缀为 'ocid1.generativeaiendpoint.oc1.us-chicago-1'）将作为您的模型 ID。

访问专属 AI 集群托管的模型时，您需要使用两个额外必填参数（"provider" 和 "context_size"）来初始化 OCIGenAI 接口。

In [ ]:
Copied! 
from llama_index.llms.oci_genai import OCIGenAI
from llama_index.core.llms import ChatMessage

llm = OCIGenAI(
    model="ocid1.generativeaiendpoint.oc1.us-chicago-1....",
    service_endpoint="https://inference.generativeai.us-chicago-1.oci.oraclecloud.com",
    compartment_id="DEDICATED_COMPARTMENT_OCID",
    auth_profile="MY_PROFILE",  # replace with your profile name,
    auth_file_location="MY_CONFIG_FILE_LOCATION",  # replace with file location where profile name configs present
    provider="MODEL_PROVIDER",  # e.g., "cohere" or "meta"
    context_size="MODEL_CONTEXT_SIZE",  # e.g., 128000
)

messages = [
    ChatMessage(
        role="system", content="You are a pirate with a colorful personality"
    ),
    ChatMessage(role="user", content="Tell me a story"),
]

resp = llm.chat(messages)
print(resp)
from llama_index.llms.oci_genai import OCIGenAI from llama_index.core.llms import ChatMessage llm = OCIGenAI( model="ocid1.generativeaiendpoint.oc1.us-chicago-1....", service_endpoint="https://inference.generativeai.us-chicago-1.oci.oraclecloud.com", compartment_id="DEDICATED_COMPARTMENT_OCID", auth_profile="MY_PROFILE", # replace with your profile name, auth_file_location="MY_CONFIG_FILE_LOCATION", # replace with file location where profile name configs present provider="MODEL_PROVIDER", # e.g., "cohere" or "meta" context_size="MODEL_CONTEXT_SIZE", # e.g., 128000 ) messages = [ ChatMessage( role="system", content="You are a pirate with a colorful personality" ), ChatMessage(role="user", content="Tell me a story"), ] resp = llm.chat(messages) print(resp)

llamaindex 中的基础工具调用功能¶

目前仅 Cohere 支持工具调用

使用 chat_with_tools 进行工具调用。

In [ ]:
Copied! 
from llama_index.llms.oci_genai import OCIGenAI
from llama_index.core.tools import FunctionTool

llm = OCIGenAI(
    model="MY_MODEL",
    service_endpoint="https://inference.generativeai.us-chicago-1.oci.oraclecloud.com",
    compartment_id="MY_OCID",
)


def multiply(a: int, b: int) -> int:
    """Multiple two integers and returns the result integer"""
    return a * b


def add(a: int, b: int) -> int:
    """Addition function on two integers."""
    return a + b


add_tool = FunctionTool.from_defaults(fn=add)
multiply_tool = FunctionTool.from_defaults(fn=multiply)

response = llm.chat_with_tools(
    tools=[add_tool, multiply_tool],
    user_msg="What is 3 * 12? Also, what is 11 + 49?",
    allow_parallel_tool_calls=True,
)

print(response)
tool_calls = response.message.additional_kwargs.get("tool_calls", [])
print(tool_calls)
from llama_index.llms.oci_genai import OCIGenAI from llama_index.core.tools import FunctionTool llm = OCIGenAI( model="MY_MODEL", service_endpoint="https://inference.generativeai.us-chicago-1.oci.oraclecloud.com", compartment_id="MY_OCID", ) def multiply(a: int, b: int) -> int: """Multiple two integers and returns the result integer""" return a * b def add(a: int, b: int) -> int: """Addition function on two integers.""" return a + b add_tool = FunctionTool.from_defaults(fn=add) multiply_tool = FunctionTool.from_defaults(fn=multiply) response = llm.chat_with_tools( tools=[add_tool, multiply_tool], user_msg="What is 3 * 12? Also, what is 11 + 49?", allow_parallel_tool_calls=True, ) print(response) tool_calls = response.message.additional_kwargs.get("tool_calls", []) print(tool_calls)

使用聊天进行工具调用

In [ ]:
Copied! 
from llama_index.llms.oci_genai import OCIGenAI
from llama_index.core.llms import ChatMessage, MessageRole

llm = OCIGenAI(
    model="MY_MODEL",
    service_endpoint="https://inference.generativeai.us-chicago-1.oci.oraclecloud.com",
    compartment_id="MY_OCID",
)


def multiply(a: int, b: int) -> int:
    """Multiple two integers and returns the result integer"""
    return a * b


def add(a: int, b: int) -> int:
    """Addition function on two integers."""
    return a + b


add_tool = FunctionTool.from_defaults(fn=add)
multiply_tool = FunctionTool.from_defaults(fn=multiply)

user_msg = ChatMessage(
    role=MessageRole.USER, content="What is 3 * 12? Also, what is 11 + 49?"
)

response = llm.chat(
    messages=[user_msg],
    tools=[multiply_tool, add_tool],
)

print(response)
tool_calls = response.message.additional_kwargs.get("tool_calls", [])
print(tool_calls)
from llama_index.llms.oci_genai import OCIGenAI from llama_index.core.llms import ChatMessage, MessageRole llm = OCIGenAI( model="MY_MODEL", service_endpoint="https://inference.generativeai.us-chicago-1.oci.oraclecloud.com", compartment_id="MY_OCID", ) def multiply(a: int, b: int) -> int: """Multiple two integers and returns the result integer""" return a * b def add(a: int, b: int) -> int: """Addition function on two integers.""" return a + b add_tool = FunctionTool.from_defaults(fn=add) multiply_tool = FunctionTool.from_defaults(fn=multiply) user_msg = ChatMessage( role=MessageRole.USER, content="What is 3 * 12? Also, what is 11 + 49?" ) response = llm.chat( messages=[user_msg], tools=[multiply_tool, add_tool], ) print(response) tool_calls = response.message.additional_kwargs.get("tool_calls", []) print(tool_calls)
